50 degrees.","url":"https://addapinch.com/how-to-make-meringue-recipe/#wprm-recipe-31426-step-0-2"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Pour eggs whites into a spotlessly-clean bowl.","name":"Pour eggs whites into a spotlessly-clean bowl.","url":"https://addapinch.com/how-to-make-meringue-recipe/#wprm-recipe-31426-step-0-3"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Whip the egg whites until they are glossy and smooth, then add the cream of tartar to help the egg whites hold their form.","name":"Whip the egg whites until they are glossy and smooth, then add the cream of tartar to help the egg whites hold their form.","url":"https://addapinch.com/how-to-make-meringue-recipe/#wprm-recipe-31426-step-0-4"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Slowly add the sugar to the egg whites about a tablespoon at a time, beating after each addition until the sugar is incorporated. Continue beating until stiff peaks form.","name":"Slowly add the sugar to the egg whites about a tablespoon at a time, beating after each addition until the sugar is incorporated. Continue beating until stiff peaks form.","url":"https://addapinch.com/how-to-make-meringue-recipe/#wprm-recipe-31426-step-0-5"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Spread meringue on top of pre-baked or no-bake dessert, place about 4 inches under the heat and bake for about 10 minutes, until golden.","name":"Spread meringue on top of pre-baked or no-bake dessert, place about 4 inches under the heat and bake for about 10 minutes, until golden.","url":"https://addapinch.com/how-to-make-meringue-recipe/#wprm-recipe-31426-step-0-6"}],"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":"4.88","ratingCount":"32"},"recipeCategory":["Dessert"],"keywords":"how to make meringue, meringue, meringue recipe","@id":"https://addapinch.com/how-to-make-meringue-recipe/#recipe","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://addapinch.com/how-to-make-meringue-recipe/#article"},"mainEntityOfPage":"https://addapinch.com/how-to-make-meringue-recipe/#webpage"}]}
